âœ… Final Summary for GitHub
This study demonstrates that integrating morphometric analysis, traditional ML, deep learning, and segmentation-enhanced multimodal pipelines provides highly accurate differentiation between DLBCL and ENKTCL. 
The ResNet50 + segmented patches model achieved the best and most stable performance across all internal and external validations, surpassing standard CNN architectures and approaching expert-level diagnostic agreement.
